      "Update T-061 in tests/state.test.ts to spy on `handle.sync` (the modern path) rather than `fs.fsyncSync`, then drop the `fs.fsyncSync(handle.fd)` line in production. The unused `import * as fs from 'node:fs';` at the top of state.ts can be removed once that's the only fs.* reference. Carry-forward to cycle 4.",
